             was indicted for <rs id="t18250915-262-off1406" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18250915-262-off1406" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18250915-262-off1406" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18250915-262-cd1407" type="crimeDate">11th of July</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18250915-262-off1406 t18250915-262-cd1407"></join>, a handkerchief, value 5 s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18250915-262-victim1330" type="victimName">
                        John 
                        Tilley
                     <interp inst="t18250915-262-victim1330" type="surname" value="Tilley"></interp>
